{"title":"舞台很小，也很大——贺第二届中国国际民间艺术节","authors":["沈鹏"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":8,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞台很小，也很大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——贺第二届中国国际民间艺术节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞台很大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也很小"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界在靠拢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界在扩充"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史在聚焦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史在延伸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大洲的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向未来的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大洋的浪潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平发展的强音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞台很小"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也很大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我面对着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座旋转的舞台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转的连衣裙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依附着地球的轴心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着无限的时空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤然——请看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“长征”—“澳星”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与舞台的强光灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同步照明"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}